    <div class="content-head">Graduate Student Researcher, Institute of Transportation Studies   <span class="smallHead"> | UC Irvine, Irvine, CA, USA</span></div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>From 5/2008 to 12/2010:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Study fundamental traffic flow theory concepts and methods</li>
        <li>Evaluate the reliability and efficiency of broadcasting in vehicular ad-hoc network using the ns-2 network simulator</li>
        <li>Analyze the delay-time constraint, communication capacity, and performance measures of IEEE 802.11p</li>
      </ul>
